Imo none of the reworks are worse than their original and are rather much healthier.
Most of the people bitching about them are either:

 A. Pre-rework mains who liked abusing a dumb kit for an unpopular champ that was strong only in their hands- {{champion:84}} {{champion:6}} 
or B. People who didn't know how Atrocious they were to deal with pre-rework - {{champion:84}} {{champion:39}} {{champion:10}} 

I personally don't see much difference between Pre-rework and Post-rework champs besides their player-base increasing because they're actually interesting now and they're not absurdly dumb to deal with...Except for Irelia but she's always been like that.

Edit: I forgot Rek'sai, she was definitely better before. I love her new ult but whatever Riot did to her numbers due to the change really crippled her.

Almost every rework has been an improvement.  The ones that have been bad have been champions who were problematic in the first place {{champion:7}} {{champion:107}} 

